# Unicode.GeneralCategory.privateUse

**Case**

A private-use character.

## Declaration

```swift
case privateUse
```

## Discussion

This value corresponds to the category `Private_Use` (abbreviated `Co`) in the [https://unicode.org/reports/tr44/#General_Category_Values].
